																		<td valign="top"
																			style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #333333; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><p>
																				In the last couple of years, the awareness about
																				financial planning has increased tremendously in
																				India. With the rise of knowledge about the field
																				the interest of people wanting to enter the industry
																				has also increased, which augurs well for the Indian
																				market since it has been thus far under served with
																				financial planners.<br /> <br /> With a vision to
																				assist financial planners with the apt support and
																				infrastructure, Ffreedom Financial Planners has
																				launched <a href="http://www.advisoroffice.in/"
																					target="_blank">Advisor Office</a>.<br /> <br />
																				Advisor Office was conceived keeping in mind
																				individuals who have the need to provide their
																				clients with a high degree of comprehensive advice
																				&amp; service levels but are not able to take the
																				leap due to lack of various support systems. In a
																				short period Advisor Office has managed to attract a
																				lot of talent who have started their practice and
																				living their dream.<br /> <br /> Advisor Office
																				consists of People, Process and Technology. Through
																				this combination it provides financial planners with
																				360 degree back office support and helps them
																				establish their Financial Planning Practice in a
																				professional way.<br /> <br /> Some of the key
																				highlights of Advisor Office include research backed
																				customized advisory and plan writing platform,
																				qualified and trained support team, marketing and
																				business development resources, integrated
																				technology and secure platform to create and manage
																				client information, practice management tools and
																				regular trainings to upgrade skills as a financial
																				planner.
																			</p>
